The results of Raman spectra showed CD existing. Meanwhile, HRTEM showed that CD and Fe3O4 nanoparticles were uniform, mono-dispersed sphere or hemisphere particles with an average size of approximately 3 nm, and particle size of CD@Fe3O4 were mainly in range of 20–30 nm (Fig. 1
                        ). UV–Vis spectrum of CD and CD@Fe3O4 are shown in Fig. 2
                        . Under white light, CD solution was in light yellow and the solution exhibits bright fluorescence light under the excitation of 365 nm. XRD results showed the nanoparticles were composed of Fe3O4 and CD@Fe3O4 (Fig. 3
                        ).
